561
00:31:46,550 --> 00:31:47,910
Later I'll drink a few

562
00:31:47,930 --> 00:31:49,000
more cups with you

563
00:31:49,030 --> 00:31:50,960
to express everything I can't say.

564
00:31:52,000 --> 00:31:53,240
Back in the army,

565
00:31:53,260 --> 00:31:54,740
Your Highness never touched
a drop at victory banquets.

566
00:31:54,740 --> 00:31:55,930
But today is your wedding,

567
00:31:55,930 --> 00:31:57,310
so you can't turn us down again!

568
00:31:57,310 --> 00:31:58,030
Exactly!

569
00:31:58,080 --> 00:31:58,930
Come on, Your Highness!

570
00:31:58,930 --> 00:31:59,250
Here, Your Highness!

571
00:31:59,250 --> 00:32:00,730
Alright, alright, alright.

572
00:32:00,730 --> 00:32:01,050
Come.

573
00:32:01,050 --> 00:32:02,050
I know Xu

574
00:32:02,050 --> 00:32:03,890
is strict in the army and cold by nature.

575
00:32:03,890 --> 00:32:04,690
Normally,

576
00:32:04,710 --> 00:32:06,180
you wouldn't dare overstep.

577
00:32:06,180 --> 00:32:07,910
But today, you've seized
the chance to have fun,

578
00:32:07,910 --> 00:32:09,240
hoping to get him drunk.

579
00:32:10,690 --> 00:32:11,450
In that case, while Xu

580
00:32:11,450 --> 00:32:12,720
is still sober,

581
00:32:12,740 --> 00:32:14,660
I'd better give him
a few proper words of advice.

582
00:32:14,660 --> 00:32:15,320
Fine.

583
00:32:27,080 --> 00:32:28,160
Can't deny it.

584
00:32:28,350 --> 00:32:30,280
His Highness is quite thoughtful.

585
00:32:30,400 --> 00:32:31,700
Of course a husband

586
00:32:31,840 --> 00:32:34,330
should be considerate
and attentive to his wife.

587
00:32:34,330 --> 00:32:35,500
Naturally.

588
00:32:35,530 --> 00:32:36,550
Otherwise, how could His Highness

589
00:32:36,550 --> 00:32:39,280
have gone personally
to the mansion to fetch you?

590
00:32:40,130 --> 00:32:41,430
He didn't

591
00:32:41,460 --> 00:32:43,330
even tell me beforehand.

592
00:32:43,350 --> 00:32:44,690
His Highness must have worried
you'd overexert yourself,

593
00:32:44,690 --> 00:32:45,820
so he came on his own.

594
00:32:45,970 --> 00:32:48,370
With him here,
who would dare make trouble?

595
00:32:52,560 --> 00:32:54,490
For His Highness to act this way...

596
00:32:56,050 --> 00:32:57,750
He must truly care about me.

597
00:32:58,310 --> 00:33:00,340
So attentive and considerate,

598
00:33:00,400 --> 00:33:01,860
always paying attention.

599
00:33:02,400 --> 00:33:03,930
If this isn't affection,

600
00:33:03,930 --> 00:33:05,130
what else could it be?

601
00:33:09,600 --> 00:33:10,360
Yu.

602
00:33:10,730 --> 00:33:11,400
Are you really up to something,

603
00:33:11,400 --> 00:33:12,590
or just being mysterious again?

604
00:33:12,590 --> 00:33:14,190
You'll find out soon enough.

605
00:33:20,300 --> 00:33:21,140
Lord Liu,

606
00:33:21,870 --> 00:33:24,490
without you these past few years,
the Ministry of Revenue

607
00:33:24,490 --> 00:33:25,980
wouldn't have made it.

608
00:33:26,640 --> 00:33:27,290
You know it's true.

609
00:33:27,290 --> 00:33:27,840
You go ahead first.

610
00:33:27,840 --> 00:33:28,600
Thanks to you.

611
00:33:28,600 --> 00:33:29,800
I'll be right behind.

612
00:33:31,280 --> 00:33:33,430
Since Lord Liu took office,

613
00:33:33,530 --> 00:33:35,930
the messy accounts
that had piled up for years

614
00:33:35,930 --> 00:33:37,700
have mostly been cleared.

615
00:33:37,840 --> 00:33:39,770
Lord Liu is truly experienced.

616
00:33:40,040 --> 00:33:41,320
Just a few days ago,

617
00:33:41,350 --> 00:33:43,980
His Majesty personally
praised him by name.

618
00:33:45,970 --> 00:33:47,400
Lord Liu has always been diligent,

619
00:33:47,400 --> 00:33:48,580
conscientious and meticulous.

620
00:33:48,580 --> 00:33:51,360
He hasn't missed
a single roll call all year.

621
00:33:51,450 --> 00:33:52,400
With him around,

622
00:33:52,420 --> 00:33:53,560
the Ministry of Revenue

623
00:33:53,560 --> 00:33:55,310
has had no issues for years.

624
00:33:55,690 --> 00:33:56,530
Indeed.

625
00:33:56,690 --> 00:33:57,490
But,

626
00:33:57,810 --> 00:33:59,080
Lord Liu, why weren't you

627
00:33:59,080 --> 00:34:00,740
seen on night duty yesterday?

628
00:34:00,770 --> 00:34:03,370
Were you perhaps meeting with

629
00:34:03,370 --> 00:34:05,530
some young lady after sunset?

630
00:34:08,010 --> 00:34:09,370
Congratulations, Your Highness.

631
00:34:09,370 --> 00:34:10,969
Best wishes on your wedding.

632
00:34:26,199 --> 00:34:28,130
Congratulations, Your Highness.

633
00:34:35,810 --> 00:34:36,489
Your Highness, please.

634
00:34:36,489 --> 00:34:38,690
I hope the hospitality wasn't lacking.

635
00:34:39,080 --> 00:34:40,600
I shall toast you all with tea

636
00:34:40,600 --> 00:34:41,530
in place of wine.

637
00:34:42,489 --> 00:34:43,929
Your Highness honors us.

638
00:34:45,679 --> 00:34:46,280
Lord Liu.

639
00:34:47,600 --> 00:34:48,239
Please.

640
00:35:09,380 --> 00:35:10,840
Thank you, Your Highness.

641
00:35:22,340 --> 00:35:23,800
Please enjoy yourselves.

642
00:35:27,120 --> 00:35:28,580
Thank you, Your Highness.

643
00:35:29,270 --> 00:35:30,730
Thank you, Your Highness.

644
00:35:42,450 --> 00:35:43,450
Since when do you have dealings

645
00:35:43,450 --> 00:35:45,110
with the Ministry of Revenue?

646
00:35:46,010 --> 00:35:48,010
It's a wedding day.
Let's not talk about anything else.

647
00:35:48,010 --> 00:35:49,540
Drinking is the main event.

648
00:35:52,200 --> 00:35:54,050
I've searched high and low

649
00:35:54,050 --> 00:35:55,200
to get this fine bottle.

650
00:35:55,200 --> 00:35:56,050
I've been saving it for today,

651
00:35:56,050 --> 00:35:57,560
to drink heartily with all of you.

652
00:35:57,560 --> 00:35:59,240
The banquet starts at 8:30 p.m.

653
00:35:59,240 --> 00:36:01,010
Lu, are you so eager for wine?

654
00:36:01,600 --> 00:36:02,490
You can't wait?

655
00:36:03,460 --> 00:36:04,810
If you want to drink, do it yourself.

656
00:36:04,810 --> 00:36:06,120
Xu stayed up all night

657
00:36:06,120 --> 00:36:07,120
to save the princess consort.

658
00:36:07,120 --> 00:36:08,270
He hasn't slept a wink.

659
00:36:08,270 --> 00:36:09,160
If he starts drinking now,

660
00:36:09,160 --> 00:36:10,720
how will he perform...

661
00:36:11,810 --> 00:36:14,210
When he enters the bridal chamber tonight?

662
00:36:14,330 --> 00:36:15,310
I invited him here

663
00:36:15,310 --> 00:36:16,790
not just for drinks.

664
00:36:17,120 --> 00:36:19,280
I really have something important to say.

665
00:36:19,280 --> 00:36:19,880
Xu,

666
00:36:20,240 --> 00:36:21,050
I know

667
00:36:21,080 --> 00:36:23,370
you've fought valiantly
on the northern frontier,

668
00:36:23,370 --> 00:36:23,970
but when it comes to

669
00:36:23,970 --> 00:36:25,640
the ways of husband and wife,

670
00:36:26,370 --> 00:36:29,120
you might still be a novice.

671
00:36:29,930 --> 00:36:31,330
Yu is right.

672
00:36:31,630 --> 00:36:34,290
In this area, you really
ought to listen to us...

673
00:36:35,030 --> 00:36:35,880
To them.

674
00:36:36,640 --> 00:36:37,120
To him.

675
00:36:41,420 --> 00:36:41,970
Right.

676
00:36:42,560 --> 00:36:43,280
Xu.

677
00:36:43,550 --> 00:36:44,810
Now that you're married,

678
00:36:44,810 --> 00:36:45,970
on your wedding night,

679
00:36:45,970 --> 00:36:46,930
you mustn't be too distant

680
00:36:46,930 --> 00:36:47,850
with your wife.

681
00:36:48,240 --> 00:36:49,100
Think about it.

682
00:36:49,600 --> 00:36:51,680
You'll be sharing a bed now.

683
00:36:52,280 --> 00:36:53,560
She's shy.

684
00:36:53,930 --> 00:36:55,200
You can't treat her
like you do everyone else,

685
00:36:55,200 --> 00:36:56,240
so silent and withdrawn.

686
00:36:56,240 --> 00:36:56,630
That...

687
00:36:56,630 --> 00:36:57,320
Exactly!

688
00:36:57,340 --> 00:36:58,820
Saying a few more words

689
00:36:58,850 --> 00:36:59,930
won't kill you.

690
00:37:00,620 --> 00:37:01,540
Bad luck.

691
00:37:01,890 --> 00:37:03,200
What an unlucky word

692
00:37:03,200 --> 00:37:04,890
to say on a wedding day!

693
00:37:04,890 --> 00:37:05,560
In short,

694
00:37:05,560 --> 00:37:06,890
just follow my advice.

695
00:37:07,280 --> 00:37:08,330
Talk about things

696
00:37:08,360 --> 00:37:09,720
she likes.

697
00:37:10,200 --> 00:37:12,270
And absolutely
don't mention war or military matters.

698
00:37:12,270 --> 00:37:13,710
You can speak to her about

699
00:37:13,730 --> 00:37:15,180
poetry, music, art, and literature.

700
00:37:15,180 --> 00:37:16,160
You're not clueless.

701
00:37:16,160 --> 00:37:18,290
Exactly. You've got to say something.

702
00:37:18,410 --> 00:37:19,810
You can't just

703
00:37:20,280 --> 00:37:21,740
get straight to the point.

704
00:37:24,810 --> 00:37:25,760
Listening to you two,

705
00:37:25,760 --> 00:37:27,420
you sound like seasoned pros.

706
00:37:27,540 --> 00:37:29,520
How many wives

707
00:37:30,120 --> 00:37:31,720
and concubines have you had?

708
00:37:32,430 --> 00:37:34,430
We haven't married,

709
00:37:34,460 --> 00:37:35,570
but in this area,

710
00:37:35,640 --> 00:37:37,700
we still understand more than you do.

711
00:37:45,380 --> 00:37:49,010
The phoenix and the dragon,
with modest wine,

712
00:37:49,060 --> 00:37:51,050
await your honorable presence.

713
00:37:52,080 --> 00:37:55,760
Esteemed guests,
please proceed to the banquet hall.

714
00:38:19,780 --> 00:38:20,570
My Lady.

715
00:38:21,970 --> 00:38:24,320
My Lady.

716
00:38:25,610 --> 00:38:27,070
His Highness is on his way.

717
00:38:28,370 --> 00:38:30,320
His Highness is almost here.

718
00:38:36,630 --> 00:38:37,290
Here.

719
00:39:16,890 --> 00:39:18,950
-Your Highness.
-Princess Consort.

720
00:39:25,990 --> 00:39:27,650
Please speak, Your Highness.

721
00:39:30,490 --> 00:39:31,950
Your abduction last night

722
00:39:32,190 --> 00:39:33,500
was due to my failure.

723
00:39:34,870 --> 00:39:36,530
Thankfully, you were clever,

724
00:39:37,080 --> 00:39:37,880
and left clues

725
00:39:38,200 --> 00:39:39,160
along the way

726
00:39:39,500 --> 00:39:40,750
that led me to you.

727
00:39:41,780 --> 00:39:43,380
Otherwise, today's wedding

728
00:39:43,490 --> 00:39:44,890
would not have happened.

729
00:39:46,160 --> 00:39:47,820
Your Highness overstates it.

730
00:39:47,930 --> 00:39:49,600
If not for your timely arrival,

731
00:39:49,600 --> 00:39:51,000
how could I have escaped?

732
00:39:51,280 --> 00:39:53,200
You've saved me time and again,

733
00:39:53,240 --> 00:39:54,310
and I have no way to repay you,

734
00:39:54,310 --> 00:39:55,570
except with myself...

735
00:40:05,050 --> 00:40:06,580
You haven't slept all night

736
00:40:08,160 --> 00:40:09,290
and was frightened.

737
00:40:10,370 --> 00:40:11,630
You must be exhausted.

738
00:40:12,600 --> 00:40:13,660
It's getting late.

739
00:40:14,080 --> 00:40:15,010
You should rest.

740
00:40:20,830 --> 00:40:21,870
Sleep now?

741
00:40:27,200 --> 00:40:28,010
You won't?

742
00:40:29,280 --> 00:40:31,010
You still have something to do?

743
00:40:35,300 --> 00:40:35,720
I...

744
00:40:36,990 --> 00:40:37,670
I...

745
00:40:39,450 --> 00:40:41,330
I can have something to do.

746
00:40:41,800 --> 00:40:42,340
But...

747
00:40:44,190 --> 00:40:46,110
But I haven't thought it through.

748
00:41:10,810 --> 00:41:11,670
Your Highness.

749
00:41:25,260 --> 00:41:25,850
This...

750
00:41:26,720 --> 00:41:27,850
This isn't mine!

751
00:41:38,530 --> 00:41:40,310
I swear it's not mine.

752
00:41:41,600 --> 00:41:44,070
Your Highness,
I really didn't put that there!

753
00:41:44,070 --> 00:41:44,680
This...

754
00:41:44,910 --> 00:41:46,500
There's no need to explain.

755
00:41:46,580 --> 00:41:47,890
I understand.

756
00:41:48,710 --> 00:41:50,170
What do you understand?

757
00:41:50,200 --> 00:41:51,700
This booklet has nothing to do with me.

758
00:41:51,700 --> 00:41:53,670
I have to make that clear.

759
00:41:53,730 --> 00:41:55,390
Even if it was prepared by you,

760
00:41:55,970 --> 00:41:57,030
it doesn't matter.

761
00:42:01,710 --> 00:42:03,760
Why did I sign the contract?

762
00:42:04,170 --> 00:42:05,710
Now look what's happened.

763
00:42:05,740 --> 00:42:07,640
Not only did it push him away,

764
00:42:08,120 --> 00:42:09,120
it made him think

765
00:42:09,120 --> 00:42:10,330
I'm being two-faced,

766
00:42:10,770 --> 00:42:12,360
saying no but meaning yes.

767
00:42:17,980 --> 00:42:18,980
Come, come, come!

768
00:42:19,050 --> 00:42:20,200
On such a joyful day,

769
00:42:20,380 --> 00:42:21,940
let's toast!

770
00:42:34,020 --> 00:42:35,940
The last time we drank this freely

771
00:42:36,300 --> 00:42:38,090
was years ago.

772
00:42:39,390 --> 00:42:41,100
I still remember when we first

773
00:42:41,240 --> 00:42:42,930
entered court service;

774
00:42:43,270 --> 00:42:45,230
how full of spirit we were.

775
00:42:47,330 --> 00:42:48,330
In a blink,

776
00:42:49,680 --> 00:42:50,560
decades

777
00:42:51,210 --> 00:42:53,130
have passed.

778
00:42:58,080 --> 00:42:58,970
Why are you

779
00:42:59,980 --> 00:43:01,690
so quiet today?

780
00:43:02,200 --> 00:43:03,080
Could it be

781
00:43:03,330 --> 00:43:05,490
that you still can't bear to part with Tan?

782
00:43:05,490 --> 00:43:06,370
Come, come.

783
00:43:06,760 --> 00:43:09,160
Have a drink to ease your sorrow.

784
00:43:10,010 --> 00:43:11,270
Let's drink together.

785
00:43:12,540 --> 00:43:13,080
Here.

786
00:43:21,160 --> 00:43:21,960
Pour the wine.

787
00:43:24,510 --> 00:43:25,000
Okay.

788
00:43:25,530 --> 00:43:26,330
Please.

789
00:43:31,410 --> 00:43:32,490
Last night,

